</CENTER><BR><TABLE WIDTH=95%><TR><TD><B><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/bforgottentruthforeignlegion><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Forgotten Truth Foreign Legion</FONT></A></B><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B>> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>General</FONT></A></B><BR><B>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B>> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>So long, and thanks for all the fish!</FONT></B></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddTopicScreenFromWeb><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/newTopic1.gif border=0></A>&nbsp; &nbsp; <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=509.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/addReply1.gif border=0></A></TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showMessage?topicID=518.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1><< Prev Topic</FONT></A> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showMessage?topicID=514.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Next Topic >></FONT></A> </TD></TR></TABLE><table border=0 width=95% cellpadding=5 cellspacing=1><TR><TD valign=top><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000000>Author</FONT><B></TD><TD valign=top><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000000>Comment</FONT><B></FONT></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#6B8E23><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Wamba the Fool</FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Unregistered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>2/26/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>12:01:56 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=509.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">So long, and thanks for all the fish!</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">  I hate to say this gang, but I am going into a temporary retirement.  For a variety of reasons, the time has come for me to bid Good-bye to Dereth.<br>
<br>
When I left EQ, I was disgruntled at the game, and sorely disillusioned with the Forgotten Truth.  I made the decision to come to AC, and I have never regretted that decision.<br>
<br>
The best part of coming to Dereth was our reforming our band of adventurers into the Foreign Legion.  (I rarely referred to it as the &quot;Forgotten Truth Foreign Legion)  We were able to retain all of the Good qualities of the old guild, and avoid the Bad qualities.  I cannot judge how our parent guild is  doing in EQ at this time, but I can say with certainty that I have enjoyed EVERY minute that I got to spend with my guildmates in AC.<br>
<br>
The trouble is, time shared with my friends is almost non-existant.<br>
<br>
All things change.  I keenly anticipate rejoining the guild sometime in the future.  Perhaps in Horizons, or the long-hoped-for Middle Earth.<br>
<br>
I have no intention of completely disappearing (so don't get your hopes up), I'll keep in touch through the board and through Celeroy.<br>
<br>
May you slaughter your foes with impunity!<br>
<br>
---------------------------Wamba---------------------</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2f2f4f><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Crow</FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Unregistered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>2/26/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>11:05:09 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=509.topic&index=1><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">&lt;sigh&gt;</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Players have come and players may go and all will be missed. However for as much as all of you means to me as a player, as a character, as a friend but more importantly as a person I must say that the loss of Wamba will touch us all in the most profound manner. Dia might be a Tazmanian Devil in a fight ... Crow a mother hen ... Ghar a rock against which all tides break ... Rayna our innocence ... Eldon our Conscience ... Harl our Honor ... Majia our youth and compassion ... Celeroy our Heart. But Wamba, our Wamba, will always be the soul of our family. His wit, his charm, his expertise with mace and verse alike will be sorely missed. There is always a place for you at our campfire. I am not going to say good-bye as they are too final. Instead I'll invoke the words that are pouring from my heart at this very moment: <br>
<br>
&quot;Good hunting and safe travels my friend, until the winds of change shift and bring you amongst us once again.&quot;</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#6B8E23><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/uceleroy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Celeroy</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>ezOP</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>2/26/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>11:53:19 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=509.topic&index=2><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: &lt;sigh&gt;</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Very well-put Crow, very well-put.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2f2f4f><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Wamba</FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Unregistered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>2/27/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>1:32:21 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=509.topic&index=3><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">reply</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">You are too kind by half Crow.  And don't forget, (no pun intended) I'm going to look you up when I get to Texas later this fall.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#6B8E23><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ugharadin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gharadin</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>2/27/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>1:46:13 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=509.topic&index=4><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: reply</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I couldn't put it half as good as Crow did, so I won't even try. You'll be missed, brother; who else would sign off with a Douglas Adams quote??? I hope if your situation changes, maybe we'll get to see you again in Dereth... if not, AC2 is a-comin'!<br>
<br>
Fair winds and following seas, my friend!</font><P><P><i><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ugharadin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gharadin</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10> at: 2/27/01 2:04:55 pm</FONT><br></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2f2f4f><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/bforgottentruthforeignlegion.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dia>Dia</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>2/27/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>5:04:29 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=509.topic&index=5><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: reply</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">And who will take to me in french now? It's always the cute ones that go first. I hope to see you in the next game!</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#6B8E23><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/udeirdra.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Deirdra</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>2/28/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>7:07:58 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=509.topic&index=6><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: reply</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Sorry to see you Leave Wamba.. but at least Majia got to meet you  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
